data.title: Symptoms and risks
data.author: editor3
data.excerpt: Think you may have  symptoms of COVID-19? Get tested, stay home, and isolate yourself. To protect yourself from infection, get vaccinated, avoid crowds, and stay out of poorly ventilated indoor spaces.
